 E[xy\mid x+y]. 
 (\sigma^2+\tau^2)\cdot(x,y)=(\sigma^2z+t,\tau^2z-t), 
 (\sigma^2+\tau^2)^2xy=\sigma^2\tau^2z^2+(\tau^2-\sigma^2)zt-t^2. 
 (\sigma^2+\tau^2)^2E[xy\mid z]=\sigma^2\tau^2z^2-\tau^2\sigma^2(\sigma^2+\tau^2), 
